source.name: 2011 Annual FOIA Report
source.description: This file contains the Social Security Administration's 2011 FOIA Annual Report. The report provides detailed information regarding the number and type of FOIA cases we processed in FY 2011. It also includes data regarding time and costs associated with processing these cases.
